  dialogueLines:
  - Speaker: Barista
    Text: Careful.
  - Speaker: Rina
    Text: Some questions enter a room like thieves and then act offended when they
      are not welcomed.
  choices:
  - choiceText: Fine. I can be patient.
    nextDialogue: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 4509f7dd12b93d64db04af99d80802c7, type: 2}
    statEffect:
      creativity: 0
      empathy: 0
      plantCorruption: 0
    relationshipEffect:
      npcId: barista
      amount: 2
  - choiceText: Then stop circling and speak plainly.
